      "content": "i'm really trying to avoid the doctor if i can, it's just so much hassle. i actually have some extra albuterol tablets from my old prescription and some some blood pressure pills my brother gave me. if i just take a slightly higher dose of my inhaler now, do you think that would clear this heaviness up quickly so i can just sleep it off? i just want to feel normal again without the whole hospital trip.",
